<div id="post-361523" class="blog-post position-8 even-post"><div class="even-post-inner blog-post-inner"><h1 class="title"><a href="http://softwarelivre.org/libreoffice/blog/bug-submission-assistant">Bug submission assistant</a></h1><span class="publishing-info"><span class="date">24 de Setembro de 2011, 0:00</span><span class="author">, por Software Livre Brasil</span><span class="comments"> - <a href="/libreoffice/blog/bug-submission-assistant#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>sem comentários ainda</span></a></span></span><p>Have you seen our new and improved way of filing bugs for LibreOffice? This <a href="http://www.libreoffice.org/get-help/bug/">bug submission assistant</a> was made by the community. <img class="wp-smiley" src="http://s1.wp.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" alt=";-)" />  Some more details on it is available in <a href="http://dachary.org/?p=886">Loic&#8217;s blog post</a>.</p>
